                            <comment id="14724739" author="busbey" created="Tue, 1 Sep 2015 03:51:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;-01&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;adds non-public config &apos;hbase.regionserver.thrift.backlog&apos;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;defaults to 0, which lets the underlying implementation choose&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;changes thrift 1 and thrift 2 thread pool servers to make use of ServerSocketTransportArgs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
